{"tid":2279863,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人氣限定女團 IZ*ONE 確定12月回歸！而明年「4月解散」還未確定～","createTime":"2020-11-10T05:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T09:12:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ef4595a77414eb301b7f13776e1d66064fea1b","tid":2279863,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"IZ*ONE 若有機會續約，就暫時不用解散了！大家是怎麼想的呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新消息，選秀節目出身的人氣女團 IZ*ONE 確定在12月回歸，消息一出也讓粉絲們相當期待，除此之外，即將面臨解散的消息還有了更新的說法。<br />\n<br />\n經紀公司的相關人士表示：「IZ*ONE 正以12月發行新專輯為目標，積極準備中。」而被問到對於明年4月解散的情況，回應道：「還沒有決定是否解散，目前正在討論這個問題。」給出了延續團體壽命的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n▼萬聖節近況照<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_06f9d997d3513caa39e2b44371a58fe9/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-10/131521-883999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_06f9d997d3513caa39e2b44371a58fe9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-10%2F131521-883999.jpg&h=00c86703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 是透過選秀節目 Mnet《Produce 48》在2018年10月29日正式出道，是預計能活動2年6個月的限定組合，假如沒有續約成功的話，明年的4月團體將會解散，各自回到原本所屬的經紀公司。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7b4b486e892fb325cfd4eb707ec6afd1/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-10/131521-884000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7b4b486e892fb325cfd4eb707ec6afd1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-10%2F131521-884000.jpg&h=15d0b6ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31e1a25cd2ec2f1ca735e24e12669c3a15121e38","tid":2279863,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"很期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c6df39d04eeb795a4f26e8296af4088615b133","tid":2279863,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e1a25cd2ec2f1ca735e24e12669c3a15121e38","tid":2279863,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy"